1. There are fifty patients involved in the study.
2. The patients are seen at a fibromyalgia outpatient treatment program.
3. The patients were randomly assigned to different treatments.
4. One group of patients was assigned to a daily soy shake.
5. Another group of patients was assigned to a daily placebo shake.
6. The placebo shake is made of casein.
